               <p>This series includes a book entitled, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Bookplates of Japan</part>
                  </title>, edited by Shozo Saito, Meiji-Shobo (Tokyo, 1941). The book was a limited edition of 350 copies, of which 50 were distributed by the publisher as gifts and 300 were made available for sale. The Arts Library Special Collections department has three different copies of the book. Bookplate #37 is missing from the edition included here.</p>
